{"type":"message","id":"58abe227","parentId":"87d8d573","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:02:49.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，Tianyou.Web目前是空的。现在我需要：\n\n1. 创建SqlSugar的数据库上下文和仓储，替换EF Core\n2. 创建YARP API网关服务\n3. 添加更多微服务\n4. 升级FormService到.NET 10\n\n让我开始：\n\n首先创建SqlSugar的数据库上下文和仓储实现。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始执行云天佑项目微服务架构开发任务。首先创建SqlSugar数据访问层。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f33e2f3e3b414ad89b247a57","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Data/SqlSugar/TianyouDbContext.cs","content":"using SqlSugar;\nusing Tianyou.Core.Abstractions;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Data.SqlSugar;\n\n/// <summary>\n/// SqlSugar 数据库上下文\n/// </summary>\npublic class TianyouDbContext\n{\n    private readonly ISqlSugarClient _db;\n\n    public TianyouDbContext(ISqlSugarClient db)\n    {\n        _db = db;\n    }\n\n    public ISqlSugarClient Db => _db;\n\n    public async Task<int> SaveChangesAsync()\n    {\n        return await Task.FromResult(1);\n    }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":208,"output":317,"cacheRead":18650,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774191765280}}
